Automobile Allowance
     4.5. . Executive shall be entitled to four (4) weeks of paid vacation per calendar year, such vacation to be taken during period or periods during each such year as shall be consistent with Executive's responsibilities and (in the Company's judgment) with the Company's vacation schedule and policies for senior officers.
Vacation
     4.6. . Pursuant to the Company's customary policies in force at the time of payment, Executive shall be reimbursed, against presentation of vouchers or receipts therefore, for all authorized expenses properly incurred by Executive on the Company's behalf in the performance of Executive's duties hereunder.
