jurisdiction thereof. Any process in any action or proceeding commenced in such courts may, among other methods, be served upon the parties hereto, as applicable, by delivering or mailing the same, via registered or certified mail, return receipt requested, addressed to the Company or Executive, as applicable, at the addresses set forth herein, or such other address as may be designated in writing. Any such service by delivery or mail shall be deemed to have the same force and effect as personal service within the State of New York.
