     I. Words in the singular include the plural and words in the plural include the singular.
     II. Titles, headings (indicated by being or shown in ) and any Table of Contents are solely for convenience of reference; do not constitute a part of the instrument in which included; and do not affect such instrument's meaning, construction, or effect.
