     (g) . Notwithstanding any provision of the Agreement (including without limitation Section 6(f) thereof) and this Confirmation or any other agreement between the parties to the contrary, neither party shall net or set off its obligations under the Transaction against its rights against the other party under any other transaction or instrument.
