Exhibit 99.1
 
          This Employment Agreement (the "Agreement) made this 30th day of January, 2008, by and between Aropostale, Inc., a Delaware corporation having an office at 112 West 34 Street, New York, New York 10120 (the "Company") and Julian R. Geiger, residing at 7 Chowning Drive, Malvern, Pennsylvania 19355 (the "Executive").
th
          WHEREAS, the Executive presently serves as the Chief Executive Officer and Chairman of the Board of the Company; and
          WHEREAS, the agreements pursuant to which the Executive serves in such capacities expire on January 31, 2008; and
          WHEREAS, the Company and the Executive wish to continue the Executive's service to the Company on the terms and conditions hereinafter set forth;
          NOW, THEREFORE, in consideration of the mutual covenants and promises made herein, the parties hereto agree as follows:
