    Executive represents and warrants that neither the execution and delivery of this Agreement by Executive nor the performance by Executive of Executives obligations hereunder, shall constitute a default under or a breach of the terms of any other agreement, indenture or contract to which Executive is a party or by which Executive is bound, nor shall the execution and delivery of this Agreement by Executive or the performance of Executives duties and obligations hereunder give rise to any claim or charge against either Executive or the Company based upon any other contract, indenture or agreement to which Executive is a party or by which Executive is bound.
      
 
 
 
 
 
 
