Automobile Allowance
            4.3. . Executive shall be entitled to four (4) weeks of paid vacation per calendar year.  Such vacation shall be taken during a period or periods during each such year as shall be consistent with Executives duties and responsibilities and shall be consistent with the Companys vacation schedule and policies for senior officers in effect at the time.
Vacation
            4.4. .  Pursuant to the Companys customary policies in force at the time of payment, Executive shall be reimbursed, against presentation of vouchers or receipts therefore, for all authorized expenses properly incurred by Executive on the Companys behalf in the performance of Executives duties hereunder.
