Governing Law; Interpretation
Should there be any conflict between the provisions of the Agreement and the provisions of any Company policy, practice, other agreement, or plan document, including, but not limited to, the Companys Amended and Restated 2002 Long-Term Incentive Plan, then the provisions of this Agreement shall prevail.
 
