           This Employment Agreement (this "Agreement") effective as of December 1, 2010 (the "Effective Date"), is entered into by and between Aeropostale, Inc., a Delaware corporation (the "Company"), and Michael J. Cunningham, an individual residing at 21 Bridge Road, Nanuet, New York 10954 (the "Executive").
