ent or Event of Default exists or would arise after giving effect to such Commitment Increase.  The Borrower shall prepay any Revolving Credit Loans outstanding on the Increase Effective Date to the extent necessary to keep the outstanding Revolving Credit Loans ratable with any revised Commitment Percentages arising from any nonratable increase in the Commitments under this
Section 2-24.
 
 
 
