and the Executive has not breached any of his representations or covenants set forth herein, the Company shall pay to Executive, in addition to any other payments the Executive may be entitled to pursuant to the terms of this Agreement, the following:
All amounts payable pursuant to Sections 8.2(d)or 9(a) shall be paid to Executive in a lump sum in cash, not later than ten (10) days after the date of termination of this Agreement. Amounts, if any, payable pursuant to Section 9(b) shall be paid to Executive in a lump sum in cash, simultaneously with the payment, if any, of Annual Bonus to the Companys other executives, for the applicable Fiscal Year in which this Agreement is terminated. Shares to be issued, if any, pursuant to Section 9(c) shall be issued to Executive not later than ten (10) days after the date of termination of this Agreement.
